This paper deals with image processing and edge detection, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The use of color dipole moments also involves mathematical analysis and manipulation of data, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper may involve information retrieval (cs.IR) as it discusses the extraction of features from images.
